  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In the latest [beacon chain spec](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/tree/master/specs), we have added implementation detail for light client. By adding these details, we greatly decrease the bandwidth requirements of a light client\r\n\r\nThe following will be modified:\r\n- New entry and exit flag code in the special object type\r\n- New `deposits_penalized_in_period` and `validator_set_delta_hash_chain` fields in crystallized state\r\n- New function to add a link to the validator hash chain which is used when a validator is added or moved. This is called `add_validator_set_change_record` in spec\r\n- Finally, the logic to set entry and exit validator flag code for the special object type\r\n\r\nSee https://ethresear.ch/t/casper-ffg-and-light-clients/2957 for further justification and details\r\n\r\n",
